  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this puzzling space capsule, you can only move left and right, but any direction could be your left and right!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288510/extras/68ed95c0e31307e123e563d6c318afc3.poster.avif?t=1745607242\" width=720 height=449 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288510/extras/68ed95c0e31307e123e563d6c318afc3.webm?t=1745607242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 chapters and 90+ levels. Each of them introduces something new.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Most of the levels in the game appear in a minimal form, with no red herrings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The difficult levels in the late game come with a simplified version.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this puzzling space capsule, you can only move left and right, but any direction could be your left and right!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288510/extras/68ed95c0e31307e123e563d6c318afc3.poster.avif?t=1745607242\" width=720 height=449 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288510/extras/68ed95c0e31307e123e563d6c318afc3.webm?t=1745607242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 chapters and 90+ levels. Each of them introduces something new.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Most of the levels in the game appear in a minimal form, with no red herrings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The difficult levels in the late game come with a simplified version.</p>",
